c0000000
00:00:02.710 --> 00:00:03.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GENAU] Attention, please.</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:04.420 --> 00:00:07.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The first-class mage exam
will begin momentarily.</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:08.680 --> 00:00:11.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You will not be tested
on your own, but as a party.</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:12.140 --> 00:00:13.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The 57 exam-takers</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:13.770 --> 00:00:15.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>will be split up
into groups of three.</b></Default>

c0000005
00:01:48.780 --> 00:01:51.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire crackling]</b></Default>

c0000006
00:01:57.120 --> 00:01:59.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There, see.
I knew you could do it.</b></Default>

c0000007
00:01:59.620 --> 00:02:02.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles] Yeah, whatever.</b></Default>

c0000008
00:02:03.670 --> 00:02:05.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANNE] Lawine's rough
around the edges,</b></Default>

c0000009
00:02:05.750 --> 00:02:07.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but she somehow
always pulls me along.</b></Default>

c0000010
00:02:08.170 --> 00:02:10.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire crackling]</b></Default>

c0000011
00:02:11.760 --> 00:02:13.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] Tomorrow,
we're finally going to fight</b></Default>

c0000012
00:02:13.680 --> 00:02:14.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>our first dragon.</b></Default>

c0000013
00:02:16.140 --> 00:02:17.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're shaking, Eisen.</b></Default>

c0000014
00:02:17.680 --> 00:02:18.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't tell me you're scared.</b></Default>

c0000015
00:02:20.060 --> 00:02:21.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[EISEN] I am.
-I see.</b></Default>

c0000016
00:02:22.230 --> 00:02:23.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In that case...</b></Default>

c0000017
00:02:23.810 --> 00:02:25.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh. You are?</b></Default>

c0000018
00:02:26.150 --> 00:02:27.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN] Deeply.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:02:30.030 --> 00:02:31.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know how you feel.</b></Default>

c0000020
00:02:32.320 --> 00:02:33.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm scared, too.</b></Default>

c0000021
00:02:33.780 --> 00:02:35.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[EISEN] Hm.
-How motivational.</b></Default>

c0000022
00:02:36.160 --> 00:02:37.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Heiter chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000023
00:02:37.570 --> 00:02:39.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My plan was to mimic
other adventurers</b></Default>

c0000024
00:02:39.740 --> 00:02:41.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and inspire you with a speech.</b></Default>

c0000025
00:02:41.580 --> 00:02:42.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry.</b></Default>

c0000026
00:02:43.330 --> 00:02:44.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It doesn't seem to have worked.</b></Default>

c0000027
00:02:45.210 --> 00:02:46.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN] Don't say that.</b></Default>

c0000028
00:02:46.460 --> 00:02:48.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I feel far less nervous.</b></Default>

c0000029
00:02:48.460 --> 00:02:51.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Be yourself. It's you
we've followed, Himmel.</b></Default>

c0000030
00:02:51.420 --> 00:02:53.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Every party needs
something different.</b></Default>

c0000031
00:02:53.300 --> 00:02:55.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We would choose
your voice over a script.</b></Default>

c0000032
00:02:56.300 --> 00:02:57.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000033
00:02:57.800 --> 00:02:58.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Guess you're right.</b></Default>

c0000034
00:02:59.010 --> 00:03:04.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000035
00:03:04.140 --> 00:03:05.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Heiter was wise.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:03:05.600 --> 00:03:07.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Every party really
does need something different.</b></Default>

c0000037
00:03:11.650 --> 00:03:13.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chirping]</b></Default>

c0000038
00:03:15.150 --> 00:03:17.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We finally caught a Stille.</b></Default>

c0000039
00:03:17.160 --> 00:03:18.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank goodness.</b></Default>

c0000040
00:03:19.080 --> 00:03:20.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now we can take a breath.</b></Default>

c0000041
00:03:21.950 --> 00:03:23.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAND] Why are you so relaxed?</b></Default>

c0000042
00:03:24.040 --> 00:03:27.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even birdy knows we're only
just getting started, right?</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:28.040 --> 00:03:29.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're a target now.</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:29.630 --> 00:03:31.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our new goal is to keep
the other parties</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:31.500 --> 00:03:32.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from taking our Stille.</b></Default>

c0000046
00:03:33.510 --> 00:03:35.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At last.
Time to spill blood.</b></Default>

c0000047
00:03:35.670 --> 00:03:36.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000048
00:03:41.180 --> 00:03:42.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right, then.</b></Default>

c0000049
00:03:42.600 --> 00:03:44.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's review everything
we've learned</b></Default>

c0000050
00:03:44.140 --> 00:03:45.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from observing the Stille.</b></Default>

c0000051
00:03:45.940 --> 00:03:47.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, we confirmed
what you already told us,</b></Default>

c0000052
00:03:48.060 --> 00:03:50.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that they fly faster
than the speed of sound.</b></Default>

c0000053
00:03:50.190 --> 00:03:51.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000054
00:03:51.400 --> 00:03:52.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sonic boom]</b></Default>

c0000055
00:03:55.570 --> 00:03:58.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANNE] There's no way we could
ever dream of chasing one down.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:03:59.450 --> 00:04:01.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Plus, the little things
are tough as dragons,</b></Default>

c0000057
00:04:01.370 --> 00:04:03.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so common attack spells
have no effect on them all.</b></Default>

c0000058
00:04:04.620 --> 00:04:06.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Most restraints are useless.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:04:07.250 --> 00:04:09.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've seen that they're
very sensitive to mana.</b></Default>

c0000060
00:04:10.080 --> 00:04:12.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even when we've suppressed
our power to approach them,</b></Default>

c0000061
00:04:12.250 --> 00:04:13.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they feel us and fly away.</b></Default>

c0000062
00:04:14.010 --> 00:04:21.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000063
00:04:21.640 --> 00:04:22.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sonic boom]</b></Default>

c0000064
00:04:22.720 --> 00:04:24.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A problem far bigger
than any of those</b></Default>

c0000065
00:04:24.930 --> 00:04:27.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is that because the Stille have
practically no mana themselves,</b></Default>

c0000066
00:04:28.060 --> 00:04:29.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we don't have anything
to try and detect.</b></Default>

c0000067
00:04:30.310 --> 00:04:32.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All that to say,
there's no quick way of knowing</b></Default>

c0000068
00:04:32.520 --> 00:04:34.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>where they are
or how many there might be.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:04:35.320 --> 00:04:37.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yesterday morning, we saw three.</b></Default>

c0000070
00:04:37.320 --> 00:04:38.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If there aren't
any more than that,</b></Default>

c0000071
00:04:38.700 --> 00:04:39.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we could be in trouble.</b></Default>

c0000072
00:04:40.530 --> 00:04:42.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're probably
just being cautious</b></Default>

c0000073
00:04:42.320 --> 00:04:44.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because so many people
are after them.</b></Default>

c0000074
00:04:44.370 --> 00:04:46.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just hope they're not
cautious enough</b></Default>

c0000075
00:04:46.370 --> 00:04:47.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to hide forever.</b></Default>

c0000076
00:04:47.960 --> 00:04:50.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if we defy the odds
and find one somehow,</b></Default>

c0000077
00:04:50.370 --> 00:04:52.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we don't have any idea
how to catch it.</b></Default>

c0000078
00:04:52.790 --> 00:04:54.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can leave that duty to me.</b></Default>

c0000079
00:04:55.130 --> 00:04:57.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After you went
to sleep last night,</b></Default>

c0000080
00:04:57.090 --> 00:04:59.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I stayed up and experimented
with a spell</b></Default>

c0000081
00:04:59.300 --> 00:05:00.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that might be useful</b></Default>

c0000082
00:05:00.260 --> 00:05:01.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for getting our hands
on a Stille.</b></Default>

c0000083
00:05:01.930 --> 00:05:03.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Gotcha.
So, that's where you went.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:05:04.100 --> 00:05:05.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What kind of spell is it?</b></Default>

c0000085
00:05:05.810 --> 00:05:07.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
You already know, Kanne.</b></Default>

c0000086
00:05:07.560 --> 00:05:08.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

c0000087
00:05:09.430 --> 00:05:11.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was made
for capturing birds.</b></Default>

c0000088
00:05:12.650 --> 00:05:15.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A tribe of hunters
developed it long ago.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:05:15.190 --> 00:05:17.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The perfect example
of a folk spell.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:05:17.820 --> 00:05:19.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In their era, magic and mages</b></Default>

c0000091
00:05:19.610 --> 00:05:21.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>were far more common
than they are today.</b></Default>

c0000092
00:05:22.160 --> 00:05:24.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANNE] Wait, are we talking
about the spell</b></Default>

c0000093
00:05:24.120 --> 00:05:25.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you used to save me?</b></Default>

c0000094
00:05:25.830 --> 00:05:28.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it's for capturing birds,
why did it work on a monster?</b></Default>

c0000095
00:05:29.040 --> 00:05:30.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Folk magic is rather loose.</b></Default>

c0000096
00:05:31.120 --> 00:05:33.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As long as your target
resembles a bird,</b></Default>

c0000097
00:05:33.170 --> 00:05:34.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the spell should cooperate.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:05:34.920 --> 00:05:37.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it could restrain
that mighty beast,</b></Default>

c0000099
00:05:37.210 --> 00:05:39.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think it should work
fine on the Stille.</b></Default>

c0000100
00:05:39.510 --> 00:05:41.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why didn't you tell us
about this before now?</b></Default>

c0000101
00:05:42.180 --> 00:05:43.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we had known,
we could've caught the one</b></Default>

c0000102
00:05:44.010 --> 00:05:45.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that we almost had yesterday.</b></Default>

c0000103
00:05:45.930 --> 00:05:47.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If only it were
as simple as that.</b></Default>

c0000104
00:05:48.470 --> 00:05:49.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hm?
-Hm?</b></Default>

c0000105
00:05:49.770 --> 00:05:52.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The spell's range
is roughly 50 centimeters.</b></Default>

c0000106
00:05:52.190 --> 00:05:54.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So we would've needed to be
close enough to touch it.</b></Default>

c0000107
00:05:55.230 --> 00:05:57.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, at least
we have a clear goal now.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:05:57.320 --> 00:05:59.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How close have
we gotten to one so far?</b></Default>

c0000109
00:05:59.940 --> 00:06:01.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>About three meters
was the closest.</b></Default>

c0000110
00:06:02.280 --> 00:06:03.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The more concerning part
is that</b></Default>

c0000111
00:06:03.860 --> 00:06:05.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we haven't been able
to get within 20</b></Default>

c0000112
00:06:05.660 --> 00:06:07.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before they picked
up on our mana.</b></Default>

c0000113
00:06:07.620 --> 00:06:10.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're just one piece away
from solving the puzzle.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:06:10.620 --> 00:06:12.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE] That's a disturbingly
large piece.</b></Default>

c0000115
00:06:13.420 --> 00:06:15.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Catching a Stille
with your magic</b></Default>

c0000116
00:06:15.080 --> 00:06:16.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>might not be possible,</b></Default>

c0000117
00:06:16.380 --> 00:06:18.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but could either of you
devise a way to stop one?</b></Default>

c0000118
00:06:18.800 --> 00:06:20.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are a million ways</b></Default>

c0000119
00:06:20.130 --> 00:06:22.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>ice magic could slow down
a normal foe,</b></Default>

c0000120
00:06:22.170 --> 00:06:25.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but ours is sensitive to mana
and resistant to freezing.</b></Default>

c0000121
00:06:25.090 --> 00:06:26.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I fear it would escape</b></Default>

c0000122
00:06:26.260 --> 00:06:28.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before we could attempt
to fix it in place.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:06:28.970 --> 00:06:31.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we had access
to loads and loads of water,</b></Default>

c0000124
00:06:31.230 --> 00:06:34.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm confident we could stop
that bird dead in its tracks.</b></Default>

c0000125
00:06:35.480 --> 00:06:37.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thing is, my magic
can only control water</b></Default>

c0000126
00:06:37.940 --> 00:06:39.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that's already there.</b></Default>

c0000127
00:06:39.360 --> 00:06:42.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nifty as it would be, I can't
create water out of nothing.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:06:43.490 --> 00:06:46.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My best bet would be
to find a lake or stream.</b></Default>

c0000129
00:06:46.570 --> 00:06:48.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course, mana struggles
to penetrate</b></Default>

c0000130
00:06:48.410 --> 00:06:49.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>large bodies of water,</b></Default>

c0000131
00:06:49.580 --> 00:06:51.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I could infuse it
with my mana</b></Default>

c0000132
00:06:51.120 --> 00:06:52.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>well before we're
planning our big move.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:06:53.210 --> 00:06:55.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then, no matter
how much water there is,</b></Default>

c0000134
00:06:55.120 --> 00:06:56.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even if it's scattered
like rain,</b></Default>

c0000135
00:06:56.670 --> 00:06:58.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can manipulate it.</b></Default>

c0000136
00:06:58.170 --> 00:07:00.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Although, I guess
instilling the water with mana</b></Default>

c0000137
00:07:00.880 --> 00:07:01.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>would definitely make</b></Default>

c0000138
00:07:02.010 --> 00:07:03.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the mana-sensitive
Stille stay away.</b></Default>

c0000139
00:07:05.510 --> 00:07:06.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stay away, huh?</b></Default>

c0000140
00:07:07.720 --> 00:07:09.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're right.
They would stay away.</b></Default>

c0000141
00:07:10.430 --> 00:07:11.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Huh?
-Huh?</b></Default>

c0000142
00:07:12.100 --> 00:07:14.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have a plan
that just might work.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:07:14.270 --> 00:07:17.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000144
00:07:33.830 --> 00:07:35.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not a bad idea,</b></Default>

c0000145
00:07:35.120 --> 00:07:37.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but we would certainly
be taking a risk.</b></Default>

c0000146
00:07:37.120 --> 00:07:38.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we do this,
we'll be picking a fight</b></Default>

c0000147
00:07:38.920 --> 00:07:40.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with all the other teams.</b></Default>

c0000148
00:07:40.500 --> 00:07:43.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, but I don't think
we could catch one otherwise.</b></Default>

c0000149
00:07:44.010 --> 00:07:45.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000150
00:07:46.680 --> 00:07:48.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lawine. Are you scared?</b></Default>

c0000151
00:07:52.140 --> 00:07:53.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're gonna rip 'em
outta my head!</b></Default>

c0000152
00:07:53.770 --> 00:07:55.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would it kill you
to show some mercy?</b></Default>

c0000153
00:07:55.890 --> 00:07:57.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[groaning]
-Hm.</b></Default>

c0000154
00:07:57.810 --> 00:07:58.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE] If you're sure,</b></Default>

c0000155
00:07:59.270 --> 00:08:00.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>let's do it already.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:08:01.980 --> 00:08:04.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind whooshing]</b></Default>

c0000157
00:08:04.690 --> 00:08:05.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're so close.</b></Default>

c0000158
00:08:06.030 --> 00:08:08.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should lay low and stay
hidden until the test is over.</b></Default>

c0000159
00:08:09.490 --> 00:08:11.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Boo, that's no fun at all.</b></Default>

c0000160
00:08:11.700 --> 00:08:13.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mages shouldn't
tuck themselves away</b></Default>

c0000161
00:08:13.490 --> 00:08:14.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>'cause they're
too scared to fight.</b></Default>

c0000162
00:08:14.910 --> 00:08:16.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAND]
They also shouldn't fight</b></Default>

c0000163
00:08:16.290 --> 00:08:18.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because they're
too reckless to wait.</b></Default>

c0000164
00:08:18.290 --> 00:08:19.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs] Huh.</b></Default>

c0000165
00:08:23.050 --> 00:08:25.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Before we do anything,
we need water.</b></Default>

c0000166
00:08:26.130 --> 00:08:27.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I believe there was a lake</b></Default>

c0000167
00:08:27.800 --> 00:08:29.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the middle
of the testing area.</b></Default>

c0000168
00:08:32.760 --> 00:08:34.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Regardless of what
happens next,</b></Default>

c0000169
00:08:34.560 --> 00:08:36.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm glad we caught
a Stille so quickly.</b></Default>

c0000170
00:08:37.310 --> 00:08:39.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we can remain
in the shadows until sunset,</b></Default>

c0000171
00:08:39.890 --> 00:08:41.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we'll pass the first test.</b></Default>

c0000172
00:08:41.650 --> 00:08:42.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000173
00:08:43.520 --> 00:08:44.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What now?</b></Default>

c0000174
00:08:44.610 --> 00:08:46.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UBEL] I'm afraid
it won't be that easy.</b></Default>

c0000175
00:08:47.190 --> 00:08:49.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought this gravel
was a road at first,</b></Default>

c0000176
00:08:49.410 --> 00:08:51.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but it's actually
a dried-up riverbed.</b></Default>

c0000177
00:08:52.780 --> 00:08:54.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Unfortunately,
this isn't the first one</b></Default>

c0000178
00:08:54.780 --> 00:08:55.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we've come across.</b></Default>

c0000179
00:08:57.200 --> 00:08:58.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Say, Land?</b></Default>

c0000180
00:08:58.160 --> 00:09:00.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At the very beginning,
they mentioned something</b></Default>

c0000181
00:09:00.170 --> 00:09:01.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about a barrier, didn't they?</b></Default>

c0000182
00:09:02.170 --> 00:09:04.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes. They're standard
for these sorts of tests.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:09:04.960 --> 00:09:06.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Physical barriers so strong</b></Default>

c0000184
00:09:06.880 --> 00:09:08.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>not a speck of dust
could bleed through.</b></Default>

c0000185
00:09:09.090 --> 00:09:11.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If that's the case,
do they block water, too?</b></Default>

c0000186
00:09:12.510 --> 00:09:13.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well.</b></Default>

c0000187
00:09:13.890 --> 00:09:15.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Judging by the dryness,</b></Default>

c0000188
00:09:15.470 --> 00:09:18.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd guess this barrier
was erected over a week ago.</b></Default>

c0000189
00:09:18.890 --> 00:09:20.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] I see.</b></Default>

c0000190
00:09:20.100 --> 00:09:22.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then most of the water
will have collected in the lake</b></Default>

c0000191
00:09:22.350 --> 00:09:23.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the middle of the basin.</b></Default>

c0000192
00:09:24.440 --> 00:09:26.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We test-takers need
water to stay active.</b></Default>

c0000193
00:09:27.320 --> 00:09:28.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's like they're
exploiting the fact</b></Default>

c0000194
00:09:28.860 --> 00:09:30.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we're living creatures.</b></Default>

c0000195
00:09:30.240 --> 00:09:31.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fair observation.</b></Default>

c0000196
00:09:31.410 --> 00:09:33.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But needing water
doesn't necessarily mean</b></Default>

c0000197
00:09:33.570 --> 00:09:34.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>gathering around the lake.</b></Default>

c0000198
00:09:36.030 --> 00:09:37.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] You're right.</b></Default>

c0000199
00:09:37.330 --> 00:09:39.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because we can carry
water with us.</b></Default>

c0000200
00:09:39.790 --> 00:09:43.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But the Stille, which are also
living creatures, cannot.</b></Default>

c0000201
00:09:44.130 --> 00:09:45.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's a good point.</b></Default>

c0000202
00:09:45.750 --> 00:09:47.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Surely others
have realized this.</b></Default>

c0000203
00:09:47.920 --> 00:09:49.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's safe to assume that
they're lying in ambush</b></Default>

c0000204
00:09:49.880 --> 00:09:51.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>around the bank as we speak.</b></Default>

c0000205
00:09:52.050 --> 00:09:53.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Huh.
-Huh.</b></Default>

c0000206
00:09:53.800 --> 00:09:55.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAND] I've made our decision.</b></Default>

c0000207
00:09:55.180 --> 00:09:56.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll give up on finding water.</b></Default>

c0000208
00:09:56.850 --> 00:09:59.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I haven't had anything
to drink in ages.</b></Default>

c0000209
00:09:59.140 --> 00:10:01.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you want your poor teammate
to shrivel up and die?</b></Default>

c0000210
00:10:01.850 --> 00:10:03.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAND] We can find
a small pond.</b></Default>

c0000211
00:10:03.560 --> 00:10:04.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe a puddle.</b></Default>

c0000212
00:10:04.730 --> 00:10:06.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UBEL] Would that
even be sanitary?</b></Default>

c0000213
00:10:06.860 --> 00:10:08.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] If we boil it, perhaps.</b></Default>

c0000214
00:10:10.570 --> 00:10:11.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000215
00:10:11.690 --> 00:10:13.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000216
00:10:13.820 --> 00:10:14.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000217
00:10:14.990 --> 00:10:22.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000218
00:10:22.790 --> 00:10:23.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000219
00:10:26.960 --> 00:10:27.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000220
00:10:29.210 --> 00:10:30.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000221
00:10:30.340 --> 00:10:37.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000222
00:10:41.980 --> 00:10:43.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aren't you a thorn in my side.</b></Default>

c0000223
00:10:43.810 --> 00:10:45.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was shooting to kill, lady.</b></Default>

c0000224
00:10:46.400 --> 00:10:48.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm surprised you could
react so quickly.</b></Default>

c0000225
00:10:50.820 --> 00:10:51.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Eh, whatever.</b></Default>

c0000226
00:10:51.940 --> 00:10:53.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just leave the cage
with the Stille inside.</b></Default>

c0000227
00:10:54.360 --> 00:10:56.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And what if I tell you no?</b></Default>

c0000228
00:10:56.110 --> 00:10:58.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then I guess we don't have
any need for words.</b></Default>

c0000229
00:10:58.530 --> 00:11:01.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000230
00:11:02.290 --> 00:11:04.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[electricity crackling]</b></Default>

c0000231
00:11:04.120 --> 00:11:05.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all gasp]</b></Default>

c0000232
00:11:08.790 --> 00:11:10.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] That came from the lake.</b></Default>

c0000233
00:11:11.090 --> 00:11:12.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

c0000234
00:11:12.630 --> 00:11:18.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000235
00:11:18.930 --> 00:11:20.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000236
00:11:22.220 --> 00:11:25.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[creaking]</b></Default>

c0000237
00:11:27.850 --> 00:11:30.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shattering]</b></Default>

c0000238
00:11:34.150 --> 00:11:36.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That girl just froze
the entire lake!</b></Default>

c0000239
00:11:36.530 --> 00:11:38.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What sort of a plan
could require that?</b></Default>

c0000240
00:11:38.490 --> 00:11:40.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A seriously unfunny one!</b></Default>

c0000241
00:11:40.580 --> 00:11:41.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WIRBEL] This mana
is from a member</b></Default>

c0000242
00:11:41.830 --> 00:11:42.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the second party.</b></Default>

c0000243
00:11:44.200 --> 00:11:45.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What could they be thinking?</b></Default>

c0000244
00:11:46.160 --> 00:11:48.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>These jokers looking
to make 50 new enemies?</b></Default>

c0000245
00:11:49.170 --> 00:11:50.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sigh]</b></Default>

c0000246
00:11:50.960 --> 00:11:54.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000247
00:11:54.880 --> 00:11:57.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

c0000248
00:11:57.130 --> 00:11:58.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>C'mon, give it all you've got!</b></Default>

c0000249
00:11:59.050 --> 00:12:00.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you can't melt it,
we're done for!</b></Default>

c0000250
00:12:03.140 --> 00:12:04.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] Denken.
What should we do?</b></Default>

c0000251
00:12:05.480 --> 00:12:08.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not what they're doing,
I can tell you that much.</b></Default>

c0000252
00:12:08.480 --> 00:12:10.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Trying to melt it now
is useless.</b></Default>

c0000253
00:12:11.610 --> 00:12:13.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After such a showy
display of magic,</b></Default>

c0000254
00:12:14.280 --> 00:12:17.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the Stille won't come anywhere
near this lake again.</b></Default>

c0000255
00:12:17.610 --> 00:12:20.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At this point, we have
no choice but to steal.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:12:21.410 --> 00:12:23.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And if the second party
was bold enough</b></Default>

c0000257
00:12:23.200 --> 00:12:24.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to pull this stunt,
there is no doubt</b></Default>

c0000258
00:12:25.040 --> 00:12:27.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they will soon have
one for the taking.</b></Default>

c0000259
00:12:27.210 --> 00:12:34.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000260
00:12:36.590 --> 00:12:37.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[leaves rustling]</b></Default>

c0000261
00:12:37.920 --> 00:12:44.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000262
00:12:48.560 --> 00:12:49.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Mistress Frieren,</b></Default>

c0000263
00:12:50.060 --> 00:12:51.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what could you
possibly be doing?</b></Default>

c0000264
00:12:53.940 --> 00:12:54.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shatters]</b></Default>

c0000265
00:12:55.070 --> 00:13:00.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000266
00:13:00.660 --> 00:13:02.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I say we scatter for now.</b></Default>

c0000267
00:13:05.580 --> 00:13:07.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire roaring]</b></Default>

c0000268
00:13:08.040 --> 00:13:10.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EDEL] Hurry up!
We're running out of time!</b></Default>

c0000269
00:13:11.120 --> 00:13:12.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How foolish they are.</b></Default>

c0000270
00:13:13.040 --> 00:13:15.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If the spell the second party
used to freeze the lake</b></Default>

c0000271
00:13:15.550 --> 00:13:17.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>didn't scare off
the Stille for good,</b></Default>

c0000272
00:13:17.170 --> 00:13:18.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>these paltry efforts to melt it</b></Default>

c0000273
00:13:18.670 --> 00:13:20.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>will certainly
get the job done.</b></Default>

c0000274
00:13:20.760 --> 00:13:22.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hm.
-[DENKEN] It's safe to say</b></Default>

c0000275
00:13:22.430 --> 00:13:24.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the Stille won't return.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:13:24.260 --> 00:13:25.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Ready to go?
-Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000277
00:13:25.600 --> 00:13:26.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That way!</b></Default>

c0000278
00:13:26.600 --> 00:13:28.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Those sharp enough
to put that together</b></Default>

c0000279
00:13:28.520 --> 00:13:31.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are busy scanning the terrain
for other watering holes.</b></Default>

c0000280
00:13:31.600 --> 00:13:33.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But their mana detection
is inadequate.</b></Default>

c0000281
00:13:34.020 --> 00:13:36.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They won't be able to handle
the airborne threats.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:13:36.940 --> 00:13:37.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Amateurs.</b></Default>

c0000283
00:13:38.570 --> 00:13:39.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE MAGE 19B] Apparently,
the second party went crazy</b></Default>

c0000284
00:13:39.990 --> 00:13:41.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and froze the lake!</b></Default>

c0000285
00:13:41.150 --> 00:13:43.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are they trying
to sabotage the exam?</b></Default>

c0000286
00:13:43.490 --> 00:13:46.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sabotage it?
No. Not at all.</b></Default>

c0000287
00:13:46.790 --> 00:13:50.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is the second party's
well-laid plan.</b></Default>

c0000288
00:13:51.000 --> 00:13:53.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And until we can figure out
what that plan is,</b></Default>

c0000289
00:13:53.880 --> 00:13:55.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we won't get anywhere.</b></Default>

c0000290
00:13:55.500 --> 00:14:02.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000291
00:14:19.030 --> 00:14:21.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
This is the work of monsters.</b></Default>

c0000292
00:14:21.240 --> 00:14:28.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000293
00:14:29.870 --> 00:14:31.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] No helping them now.</b></Default>

c0000294
00:14:33.830 --> 00:14:35.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Move along.</b></Default>

c0000295
00:14:35.120 --> 00:14:36.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on, sir.</b></Default>

c0000296
00:14:36.210 --> 00:14:37.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should at least
take their bodies down.</b></Default>

c0000297
00:14:38.840 --> 00:14:41.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can see the beasts,
can't you?</b></Default>

c0000298
00:14:41.470 --> 00:14:43.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're circling
above us right now.</b></Default>

c0000299
00:14:44.840 --> 00:14:46.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not just one or two
of them, either.</b></Default>

c0000300
00:14:47.350 --> 00:14:49.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They've laid their magic
on those corpses.</b></Default>

c0000301
00:14:50.180 --> 00:14:52.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we tried to move them,
they would know we're here.</b></Default>

c0000302
00:14:53.600 --> 00:14:55.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's the way of the Geisel.</b></Default>

c0000303
00:14:55.850 --> 00:14:57.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They use the remains
of one victim</b></Default>

c0000304
00:14:57.820 --> 00:14:59.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to lure in the next.</b></Default>

c0000305
00:14:59.690 --> 00:15:02.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This party was so naive
as to fall for their trap,</b></Default>

c0000306
00:15:02.940 --> 00:15:04.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and look where it got them.</b></Default>

c0000307
00:15:05.280 --> 00:15:06.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This isn't right.</b></Default>

c0000308
00:15:06.570 --> 00:15:09.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why hold the test in a place
with such awful monsters?</b></Default>

c0000309
00:15:10.410 --> 00:15:11.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's like the proctors
don't care</b></Default>

c0000310
00:15:11.910 --> 00:15:13.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if the participants get killed.</b></Default>

c0000311
00:15:13.830 --> 00:15:15.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is obviously
your first time</b></Default>

c0000312
00:15:15.670 --> 00:15:17.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>taking the exam, Laufen.</b></Default>

c0000313
00:15:17.460 --> 00:15:19.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Their reason is rather simple.
-Hm?</b></Default>

c0000314
00:15:20.420 --> 00:15:22.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anyone who is killed
on a stage like this</b></Default>

c0000315
00:15:22.630 --> 00:15:24.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is unqualified
to be first-class.</b></Default>

c0000316
00:15:25.550 --> 00:15:27.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Continental
Magic Association</b></Default>

c0000317
00:15:27.680 --> 00:15:30.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is keen to uphold
the standards of that title.</b></Default>

c0000318
00:15:31.010 --> 00:15:33.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For many of them, the idea
of what a mage should be</b></Default>

c0000319
00:15:33.310 --> 00:15:35.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was cemented long ago
by the noble few</b></Default>

c0000320
00:15:35.480 --> 00:15:37.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who took down
the Demon King's army.</b></Default>

c0000321
00:15:38.150 --> 00:15:41.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no patience for that
outdated school of thought.</b></Default>

c0000322
00:15:41.320 --> 00:15:42.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That surprises me, Denken.</b></Default>

c0000323
00:15:43.030 --> 00:15:44.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought of all people,</b></Default>

c0000324
00:15:44.110 --> 00:15:45.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you would be the one
to take their side.</b></Default>

c0000325
00:15:46.070 --> 00:15:48.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The quality of a mage
is irrelevant.</b></Default>

c0000326
00:15:49.030 --> 00:15:50.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[LAUFEN] Hm?
-It's more important</b></Default>

c0000327
00:15:50.740 --> 00:15:53.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for first-class mages
to be symbols of power</b></Default>

c0000328
00:15:53.240 --> 00:15:54.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than powerful themselves.</b></Default>

c0000329
00:15:54.870 --> 00:15:57.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Strength means nothing
if a mage can't act</b></Default>

c0000330
00:15:57.170 --> 00:15:58.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as that symbol.</b></Default>

c0000331
00:15:58.250 --> 00:16:00.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In the real world,
casting spells weighs</b></Default>

c0000332
00:16:00.290 --> 00:16:02.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>much less than winning hearts.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:16:02.420 --> 00:16:05.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've seen countless mages
far more skilled than myself</b></Default>

c0000334
00:16:05.340 --> 00:16:07.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>fall from grace
and be persecuted</b></Default>

c0000335
00:16:07.260 --> 00:16:09.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by the same people who once
celebrated them.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:16:10.850 --> 00:16:13.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Great power's a thing
to be feared.</b></Default>

c0000337
00:16:13.180 --> 00:16:15.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And rule by fear
can only last so long.</b></Default>

c0000338
00:16:16.270 --> 00:16:20.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Neither magic nor strength
should be put on a pedestal.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:16:20.440 --> 00:16:21.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see now.</b></Default>

c0000340
00:16:21.860 --> 00:16:24.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, someone as weak
as you is perfect for the job.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:16:25.320 --> 00:16:27.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] You would be wise
to watch your tongue, whelp.</b></Default>

c0000342
00:16:27.820 --> 00:16:30.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I could beat you to a pulp
with my hands restrained</b></Default>

c0000343
00:16:30.360 --> 00:16:31.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and eyes closed.</b></Default>

c0000344
00:16:34.370 --> 00:16:35.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:16:35.870 --> 00:16:38.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000346
00:16:40.630 --> 00:16:47.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000347
00:17:03.570 --> 00:17:05.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAUFEN] Still no luck.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:17:05.110 --> 00:17:06.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The second party is good.</b></Default>

c0000349
00:17:07.320 --> 00:17:09.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] Good at concealing
their mana, at the very least.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:17:10.360 --> 00:17:11.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000351
00:17:11.660 --> 00:17:13.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's been something
eerily similar</b></Default>

c0000352
00:17:13.450 --> 00:17:15.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about every watering hole
we've come across.</b></Default>

c0000353
00:17:16.200 --> 00:17:17.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000354
00:17:17.580 --> 00:17:19.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though it's faint, I can sense</b></Default>

c0000355
00:17:19.540 --> 00:17:21.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there was mana
poured into this pond.</b></Default>

c0000356
00:17:23.000 --> 00:17:24.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't pick up on anything.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:17:24.750 --> 00:17:26.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Strange. Can you?</b></Default>

c0000358
00:17:26.960 --> 00:17:28.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not even a little.</b></Default>

c0000359
00:17:28.840 --> 00:17:30.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just what could they be up to?</b></Default>

c0000360
00:17:30.840 --> 00:17:32.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's such a small amount
of mana here</b></Default>

c0000361
00:17:32.840 --> 00:17:34.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I highly doubt
even the caster</b></Default>

c0000362
00:17:34.600 --> 00:17:36.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>could successfully detect it.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:17:36.770 --> 00:17:39.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But the Stille could
sense it without difficulty.</b></Default>

c0000364
00:17:39.980 --> 00:17:42.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They won't be coming
near this water again.</b></Default>

c0000365
00:17:42.980 --> 00:17:44.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The only reason
you would want that is...</b></Default>

c0000366
00:17:45.520 --> 00:17:47.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course!
There must be an untouched</b></Default>

c0000367
00:17:47.990 --> 00:17:49.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>watering hole somewhere.</b></Default>

c0000368
00:17:50.320 --> 00:17:51.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And if we can find that,</b></Default>

c0000369
00:17:51.950 --> 00:17:54.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we will find
the second party, as well.</b></Default>

c0000370
00:17:54.410 --> 00:17:55.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But how can we?</b></Default>

c0000371
00:17:58.120 --> 00:17:59.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm going to rest a bit.</b></Default>

c0000372
00:17:59.960 --> 00:18:01.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] Denken.</b></Default>

c0000373
00:18:01.160 --> 00:18:03.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The testing area is enormous.</b></Default>

c0000374
00:18:03.580 --> 00:18:05.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It would be impossible
to find a mage</b></Default>

c0000375
00:18:05.460 --> 00:18:07.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who truly doesn't
want to be found.</b></Default>

c0000376
00:18:08.300 --> 00:18:09.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just wait.</b></Default>

c0000377
00:18:09.460 --> 00:18:11.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They'll have to show us
where they are soon enough.</b></Default>

c0000378
00:18:15.220 --> 00:18:16.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANNE]
I think I finally did it!</b></Default>

c0000379
00:18:16.890 --> 00:18:19.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I poured mana into every pond
I could find!</b></Default>

c0000380
00:18:19.810 --> 00:18:21.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess there could be
other ones</b></Default>

c0000381
00:18:21.430 --> 00:18:22.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we don't know about, though.</b></Default>

c0000382
00:18:23.730 --> 00:18:26.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Limiting the watering holes
the Stille can use</b></Default>

c0000383
00:18:26.110 --> 00:18:27.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>should be enough
for our plan to work.</b></Default>

c0000384
00:18:28.650 --> 00:18:29.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So all that's left to do now</b></Default>

c0000385
00:18:30.070 --> 00:18:31.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is wait for one to come
and get a drink.</b></Default>

c0000386
00:18:34.530 --> 00:18:41.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000387
00:18:41.330 --> 00:18:43.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had no idea that
mana was something</b></Default>

c0000388
00:18:43.370 --> 00:18:45.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a mage could
completely turn off.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:18:45.500 --> 00:18:46.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, not completely.</b></Default>

c0000390
00:18:47.290 --> 00:18:50.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even the slightest movement
causes some mana to eke out.</b></Default>

c0000391
00:18:50.590 --> 00:18:51.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sense it?</b></Default>

c0000392
00:18:51.920 --> 00:18:53.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not at all, actually.</b></Default>

c0000393
00:18:54.630 --> 00:18:56.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kanne and I will stand watch.</b></Default>

c0000394
00:18:56.300 --> 00:18:57.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000395
00:18:59.260 --> 00:19:00.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Provided she can handle that.</b></Default>

c0000396
00:19:01.020 --> 00:19:02.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, shut up.</b></Default>

c0000397
00:19:03.060 --> 00:19:05.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it rained, I could take down
just about anybody.</b></Default>

c0000398
00:19:05.520 --> 00:19:07.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE] If it rained,
the barrier would deflect it.</b></Default>

c0000399
00:19:11.820 --> 00:19:14.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000400
00:19:15.070 --> 00:19:18.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[galloping]</b></Default>

c0000401
00:19:21.040 --> 00:19:27.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000402
00:19:32.760 --> 00:19:34.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[bird screeching]</b></Default>

c0000403
00:19:35.550 --> 00:19:38.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fluttering]</b></Default>

c0000404
00:19:38.470 --> 00:19:39.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

c0000405
00:19:39.970 --> 00:19:41.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[water splashes]</b></Default>

c0000406
00:19:42.640 --> 00:19:49.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000407
00:20:05.620 --> 00:20:10.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000408
00:20:10.290 --> 00:20:11.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Kanne gasps]</b></Default>

c0000409
00:20:14.920 --> 00:20:16.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wow, Frieren! Did you catch it?</b></Default>

c0000410
00:20:17.720 --> 00:20:20.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This was well worth picking
a fight with the other parties.</b></Default>

c0000411
00:20:20.890 --> 00:20:22.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now we're gonna
pass the first test</b></Default>

c0000412
00:20:22.390 --> 00:20:23.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with flying colors!</b></Default>

c0000413
00:20:26.270 --> 00:20:27.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or not.</b></Default>

c0000414
00:20:27.640 --> 00:20:29.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] Well, it's about time.</b></Default>

c0000415
00:20:29.690 --> 00:20:32.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One of their members
had to use magic.</b></Default>

c0000416
00:20:32.110 --> 00:20:34.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No mage, no matter
how skilled they might be,</b></Default>

c0000417
00:20:34.610 --> 00:20:37.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>can fully conceal their mana
as they wield it.</b></Default>

c0000418
00:20:38.070 --> 00:20:39.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We need to leave.</b></Default>

c0000419
00:20:39.740 --> 00:20:41.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Someone's detected us.</b></Default>

c0000420
00:20:41.490 --> 00:20:45.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000421
00:20:46.910 --> 00:20:48.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, you're certainly quick.</b></Default>

c0000422
00:20:48.410 --> 00:20:50.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So much for getting away
from here.</b></Default>

c0000423
00:20:51.040 --> 00:20:52.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, Jubelade.</b></Default>

c0000424
00:20:52.420 --> 00:20:59.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000425
00:21:01.260 --> 00:21:02.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Doragate.</b></Default>

c0000426
00:21:02.470 --> 00:21:04.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000427
00:21:04.760 --> 00:21:06.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] It's like a cannon.</b></Default>

c0000428
00:21:08.940 --> 00:21:10.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EHRE] She keeps backing off.</b></Default>

c0000429
00:21:10.560 --> 00:21:14.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000430
00:21:14.360 --> 00:21:15.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000431
00:21:17.650 --> 00:21:20.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EHRE] Her technique is refined
and near seamless,</b></Default>

c0000432
00:21:20.530 --> 00:21:21.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but it's old-fashioned.</b></Default>

c0000433
00:21:21.820 --> 00:21:23.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It feels like I'm fighting
my grandfather.</b></Default>

c0000434
00:21:25.080 --> 00:21:27.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ordinary offensive
and defensive magic?</b></Default>

c0000435
00:21:27.700 --> 00:21:29.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing more
than the most basic of spells.</b></Default>

c0000436
00:21:30.460 --> 00:21:32.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Playing things close
to the chest, are we?</b></Default>

c0000437
00:21:33.000 --> 00:21:34.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was taught
from a very young age</b></Default>

c0000438
00:21:34.630 --> 00:21:37.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to only use basic spells
during combat.</b></Default>

c0000439
00:21:37.210 --> 00:21:39.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This philosophy's coming
from your master, then?</b></Default>

c0000440
00:21:40.090 --> 00:21:42.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Yes. She said
the basics are enough</b></Default>

c0000441
00:21:42.300 --> 00:21:44.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to defeat mages of this era.</b></Default>

c0000442
00:21:45.220 --> 00:21:46.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yeah?</b></Default>

c0000443
00:21:48.890 --> 00:21:49.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000444
00:21:50.060 --> 00:21:51.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000445
00:21:52.810 --> 00:21:55.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000446
00:21:55.650 --> 00:21:56.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EHRE] Predictable.</b></Default>

c0000447
00:21:56.860 --> 00:21:58.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's so simple it feels wrong,</b></Default>

c0000448
00:21:59.150 --> 00:22:00.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>like I'm fighting a mage</b></Default>

c0000449
00:22:00.490 --> 00:22:02.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who just learned
her first spell.</b></Default>

c0000450
00:22:04.370 --> 00:22:05.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're going to struggle.</b></Default>

c0000451
00:22:06.120 --> 00:22:08.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you try to take on Wirbel
with this technique,</b></Default>

c0000452
00:22:08.660 --> 00:22:10.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you would be dead
after the first blow.</b></Default>

c0000453
00:22:11.040 --> 00:22:12.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] That doesn't
make any sense.</b></Default>

c0000454
00:22:13.210 --> 00:22:15.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought you were
the strongest one here.</b></Default>

c0000455
00:22:15.460 --> 00:22:16.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or was I wrong?</b></Default>

c0000456
00:22:16.590 --> 00:22:19.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000457
00:22:21.090 --> 00:22:23.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[rumbling]
-[wind whooshing]</b></Default>

c0000458
00:22:24.680 --> 00:22:25.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000459
00:22:26.890 --> 00:22:28.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wirbel and his men
took on the remnants</b></Default>

c0000460
00:22:28.810 --> 00:22:30.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the Demon King's army.</b></Default>

c0000461
00:22:30.520 --> 00:22:32.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's captain
of the Northern Magic Corps.</b></Default>

c0000462
00:22:33.440 --> 00:22:35.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He has far more
experience in battle.</b></Default>

c0000463
00:22:36.310 --> 00:22:39.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>His magic is utterly devoid
of character,</b></Default>

c0000464
00:22:39.150 --> 00:22:41.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>designed to win at all costs.</b></Default>

c0000465
00:22:42.240 --> 00:22:44.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I pity the girl
who's up against him now.</b></Default>

c0000466
00:22:45.280 --> 00:22:46.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She'll surely be killed.</b></Default>

c0000467
00:22:48.290 --> 00:22:49.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that so?</b></Default>

c0000468
00:24:20.420 --> 00:24:21.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UBEL]
What hells have you seen?</b></Default>

c0000469
00:24:21.960 --> 00:24:23.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] I'll crush her.</b></Default>

c0000470
00:24:23.090 --> 00:24:24.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANNE] This guy is no joke.</b></Default>

c0000471
00:24:24.090 --> 00:24:26.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE] Try me. I dare you.
[LAND] How impressive.</b></Default>

c0000472
00:24:26.090 --> 00:24:27.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] You old fool.</b></Default>

c0000473
00:24:27.300 --> 00:24:28.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WIRBEL] I've never run
from killing</b></Default>

c0000474
00:24:28.680 --> 00:24:29.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when it was necessary.</b></Default>

